you're a big phony!

269
00:10:50,333 --> 00:10:51,958
Shut your mouth, amateur!

270
00:10:52,041 --> 00:10:54,333
Don't you dare waste my
student's precious time

271
00:10:54,416 --> 00:10:55,958
with your
middle-school nonsense!

272
00:10:56,041 --> 00:10:57,125
[TOME]
What?!

273
00:10:57,208 --> 00:10:58,458
Are you saying
that you don't care

274
00:10:58,541 --> 00:10:59,958
if they shut down our club?

275
00:11:00,041 --> 00:11:02,541
