room and have nowhere to go!

276
00:11:02,625 --> 00:11:03,958
[gasps]

277
00:11:04,041 --> 00:11:06,416
[MOB] Master, the club
president is crying,

278
00:11:06,500 --> 00:11:08,541
so I think I should
join after all.

279
00:11:08,625 --> 00:11:10,833
[ARATAKA] Don't be fooled!
They're crocodile tears!

280
00:11:10,916 --> 00:11:12,083
Huh?

281
00:11:12,166 --> 00:11:14,250
[ARATAKA] Bonds, memories,
and friendship...

282
00:11:14,333 --> 00:11:15,583
It's not like any
of those things

283
00:11:15,666 --> 00:11:18,500
