I least wanna do...

319
00:12:31,625 --> 00:12:34,416
,..is to be dressed
up like this.

320
00:12:34,500 --> 00:12:35,916
Oh, there it is.

321
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:37,666
Saint Highso Girls' Academy.

322
00:12:37,750 --> 00:12:39,916
