have asked us both

324
00:12:41,583 --> 00:12:43,041
to meet up with
them on the roof.

325
00:12:43,125 --> 00:12:44,375
Right.

326
00:12:44,458 --> 00:12:46,000
Stop! What in the world
do you think you're doing?

327
00:12:46,083 --> 00:12:46,750
[ARATAKA]
Excuse me?

328
00:12:46,833 --> 00:12:47,916
