Can it, you perverted weirdo!

336
00:12:59,291 --> 00:13:00,666
I knew this wouldn't work.

337
00:13:00,750 --> 00:13:03,000
But I'm glad they saw
through our disguises.

338
00:13:03,083 --> 00:13:06,333
I didn't wanna sneak into
the school dressed like this.

339
00:13:06,416 --> 00:13:08,083
[OFFICER 2B]
That was a close one, huh?

340
00:13:08,166 --> 00:13:10,416
Now hurry along and stay
away from that freak.

341
00:13:10,500 --> 00:13:12,041
Huh?

342
00:13:12,125 --> 00:13:14,958
[OFFICER 2A] Don't you worry.
We'll deal with this phony.

343
00:13:15,041 --> 00:13:16,458
[MOB]
Uh...

344
00:13:18,875 --> 00:13:20,041
