346
00:13:32,041 --> 00:13:34,583
Won't I get in a lot of
trouble if I'm busted?

347
00:13:36,333 --> 00:13:38,291
[MOB] He said we were
supposed to meet our clients

348
00:13:38,375 --> 00:13:39,750
on the roof, but...

349
00:13:44,166 --> 00:13:45,083
