350
00:13:45,166 --> 00:13:47,083
[MOB]
Um, hello?

351
00:13:47,166 --> 00:13:48,958
I've come from the
consultation office.

352
00:13:49,041 --> 00:13:51,083
So, are you three
the clients, or uh--?

353
00:13:51,166 --> 00:13:52,833
Huh? Who in the hell are you?

354
00:13:52,916 --> 00:13:55,458
You don't look familiar.
Transfer student, right?

355
00:13:55,541 --> 00:13:57,208
--Huh?
--[GIRL 2C] Consultation office?

356
00:13:57,291 --> 00:13:58,583
You're here to see if
you can "get through"

357
00:13:58,666 --> 00:14:00,083
to us thugs, is that it?

358
00:14:00,166 --> 00:14:01,375
So annoying!

359
00:14:01,458 --> 00:14:03,125
Do you really think
we're just gonna sit here

360
00:14:03,208 --> 00:14:05,333
