like you lecture us?!

361
00:14:05,416 --> 00:14:06,791
[MOB]
No, I'm just--

362
00:14:06,875 --> 00:14:09,083
Why don't you mind your own
damn business, do-gooder?!

363
00:14:09,166 --> 00:14:11,708
If you don't, we're gonna
make you regret it!

364
00:14:11,791 --> 00:14:14,000
Sorry about that. My bad.

365
00:14:14,083 --> 00:14:15,458
Ugh. Talk about a downer.

366
00:14:15,541 --> 00:14:16,583
Let's get outta here.

367
00:14:16,666 --> 00:14:17,666
[GIRL 2B]
Hmph!

368
00:14:20,291 --> 00:14:21,291
[sighs]

369
00:14:21,375 --> 00:14:23,208
[CHIHIRO]
Hello?

370
00:14:23,291 --> 00:14:25,291
First thing you do is
get picked on by thugs.

371
00:14:25,375 --> 00:14:26,458
Way to go.

372
00:14:26,541 --> 00:14:28,875
We're the clients you're
here to meet with.

373
00:14:30,083 --> 00:14:32,291
[CHIHIRO]
Isn't that Reigen guy coming?

374
00:14:32,375 --> 00:14:34,333
He got caught up
at the front gate.

375
00:14:34,416 --> 00:14:36,750
[MARI] Also, you both
came dressed as girls?

376
00:14:36,833 --> 00:14:37,833
