377
00:14:37,916 --> 00:14:39,041
He couldn't get
permission to come in,

378
00:14:39,125 --> 00:14:40,583
so we didn't have a choice.

379
00:14:40,666 --> 00:14:41,791
[MARI]
I see.

380
00:14:41,875 --> 00:14:43,625
We're sorry to make you
go through all that.

381
00:14:43,708 --> 00:14:45,708
The school just refuses
to take us seriously

382
00:14:45,791 --> 00:14:47,708
about any of this
supernatural stuff.

383
00:14:47,791 --> 00:14:49,291
So that's why we called you.

384
00:14:49,375 --> 00:14:51,750
What exactly was it
that you told them?

385
00:14:51,833 --> 00:14:54,500
[MARI] Students' belongings
are mysteriously vanishing,

386
00:14:54,583 --> 00:14:56,375
and we've been
hearing weird noises.

387
00:14:56,458 --> 00:14:58,583
[CHIHIRO] Like, a
poltergeist or something.

388
00:14:58,666 --> 00:14:59,875
[MARI] We heard things
have been spotted

389
00:14:59,958 --> 00:15:01,791
