390
00:15:01,875 --> 00:15:02,916
[CHIHIRO]
Yeah.

391
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:04,625
Apparently a bra
started floating around

392
00:15:04,708 --> 00:15:05,750
in the locker room.

393
00:15:05,833 --> 00:15:07,291
[MOB]
A bra?

394
00:15:07,375 --> 00:15:09,375
We're sure it's not just
kids playing pranks.

395
00:15:09,458 --> 00:15:11,041
It's definitely supernatural.

396
00:15:11,125 --> 00:15:12,666
So we went online,
looked around,

397
00:15:12,750 --> 00:15:14,791
then called the cheapest
exorcist in the area

398
00:15:14,875 --> 00:15:16,833
and somehow ended up with you.

399
00:15:16,916 --> 00:15:18,333
Looks like you get
what you pay for.

400
00:15:18,416 --> 00:15:19,541
Huh?

401
00:15:19,625 --> 00:15:21,458
Can't believe a guy
was trembling so much

402
00:15:21,541 --> 00:15:23,458
just from dealing with
some high school girls.

403
00:15:23,541 --> 00:15:25,958
You must be quite the
reliable gentleman.

404
00:15:26,041 --> 00:15:27,041
[MOB]
Oh... Thank you.

405
00:15:27,125 --> 00:15:28,166
That was sarcasm, duh!

406
00:15:28,250 --> 00:15:29,791
She wasn't complimenting you!

407
00:15:29,875 --> 00:15:32,250
[MARI] Are you sure we
can trust him with this?

408
00:15:32,333 --> 00:15:36,416
[CHIHIRO] I have my doubts.
You seem pretty unreliable.

409
00:15:36,500 --> 00:15:36,958
What's up?

410
00:15:37,041 --> 00:15:38,208
Something wrong?

411
00:15:38,291 --> 00:15:40,541
[MOB]
I-It's okay...

412
00:15:40,625 --> 00:15:43,333
