perform an exorcism.

413
00:15:45,375 --> 00:15:48,541
[MARI] Now, let us know if
you feel anything spiritual.

414
00:15:48,625 --> 00:15:49,791
[MOB]
Right.

415
00:15:51,958 --> 00:15:54,166
[CHIHIRO]
Well? Do you sense anything?

416
00:15:54,250 --> 00:15:55,500
Maybe a little.

417
00:15:55,583 --> 00:15:58,000
[CHIHIRO]
Is he being serious right now?

418
00:15:59,125 --> 00:16:00,791
There. It's nearby.

419
00:16:00,875 --> 00:16:01,458
[BOTH gasp]

420
00:16:01,541 --> 00:16:02,500
Are you for real?

421
00:16:02,583 --> 00:16:04,375
[GIRL 2C screams]
Someone help!

422
00:16:04,458 --> 00:16:06,041
[BOTH gasp]

423
00:16:06,125 --> 00:16:08,208
What's going on?

424
00:16:08,291 --> 00:16:10,000
[GIRL 2C]
Something was here...

425
00:16:10,083 --> 00:16:14,250
Something was just looking in
from the top of the door...

426
00:16:14,333 --> 00:16:16,000
[CHIHIRO]
The windows are locked tight.

427
00:16:16,083 --> 00:16:19,250
And we would've seen if somebody
tried to leave through the exit.

428
00:16:19,333 --> 00:16:21,541
I'm going to follow the spirit.

429
00:16:24,625 --> 00:16:27,625
[CHIHIRO]
Whatcha got? Anything so far?

430
00:16:27,708 --> 00:16:29,958
[MARI]
So, we can trust you, right?

431
00:16:30,041 --> 00:16:31,625
[MOB]
Right.

432
00:16:31,708 --> 00:16:34,750
[MARI]
You still can't find it?

433
00:16:34,833 --> 00:16:36,250
