it might try something.

436
00:16:41,250 --> 00:16:42,916
[CHIHIRO]
Wh-What are we gonna do?

437
00:16:43,000 --> 00:16:46,000
[MARI] The basketball team
is practicing inside.

438
00:16:46,083 --> 00:16:47,458
Let's end this.

439
00:16:50,708 --> 00:16:52,541
[MOB]
I've trapped the spirit.

440
00:16:58,583 --> 00:17:02,375
[STUDENTS chattering]

441
00:17:02,458 --> 00:17:04,166
[MOB]
Found you.

442
00:17:04,250 --> 00:17:06,041
[STUDENTS chattering]

443
00:17:06,125 --> 00:17:07,500
Huh?

444
00:17:10,250 --> 00:17:10,666
[gasps]

445
00:17:10,750 --> 00:17:12,000
