446
00:17:12,083 --> 00:17:14,458
[MARI]
What is that?! A ghost?!

447
00:17:14,541 --> 00:17:17,500
Now you've done it,
you psychic brat.

448
00:17:17,583 --> 00:17:21,000
How dare you trap me
in my own haunting grounds!

449
00:17:21,083 --> 00:17:23,750
Are you going to try
to ruin my paradise?

450
00:17:23,833 --> 00:17:24,833
[STUDENTS scream]

451
00:17:24,916 --> 00:17:27,541
