is what you'll get!

452
00:17:30,250 --> 00:17:33,291
[SCENT GHOUL yells]

453
00:17:33,375 --> 00:17:35,083
[CHIHIRO, MARI scream]

454
00:17:35,166 --> 00:17:36,583
[SCENT-GHOUL grunts]

455
00:17:38,625 --> 00:17:40,250
[SCENT-GHOUL]
Crap! I underestimated

456
00:17:40,333 --> 00:17:41,833
