461
00:17:51,125 --> 00:17:52,041
[screams]

462
00:17:52,125 --> 00:17:53,958
Now, get back!

463
00:17:54,041 --> 00:17:54,666
[SCENT GHOUL]
Huh?

464
00:17:54,750 --> 00:17:55,916
[gasps]

465
00:18:00,208 --> 00:18:01,708
[SCENT GHOUL groans]

466
00:18:03,208 --> 00:18:06,333
[SCENT GHOUL groaning]

467
00:18:15,833 --> 00:18:17,250
It's all over now.

468
00:18:17,333 --> 00:18:20,666
[STUDENTS cheer]

469
00:18:20,750 --> 00:18:23,166
