Good for you, dude.

470
00:18:23,250 --> 00:18:24,208
Thanks a lot.

471
00:18:24,291 --> 00:18:26,416
You were pretty
reliable after all.

472
00:18:26,500 --> 00:18:29,541
[SCENT GHOUL]
Damn it...

473
00:18:29,625 --> 00:18:30,666
