finally found happiness.

476
00:18:37,083 --> 00:18:40,083
Honestly, you seem
to be similar to me.

477
00:18:40,166 --> 00:18:41,750
Similar?

478
00:18:41,833 --> 00:18:44,791
[SCENT GHOUL] The way you
get nervous around girls.

479
00:18:44,875 --> 00:18:48,833
