480
00:18:48,916 --> 00:18:49,750
[gasps]

481
00:18:49,833 --> 00:18:51,000
[SCENT GHOUL]
I...

482
00:18:51,083 --> 00:18:54,666
I finally started to
have fun after I died.

483
00:18:54,750 --> 00:18:56,625
I was content.

484
00:18:56,708 --> 00:18:59,958
But I guess that's all
over now. Isn't it...

485
00:19:01,791 --> 00:19:03,166
[SCENT GHOUL]
So...

486
00:19:03,250 --> 00:19:07,000
Are you living every day
to the fullest?

487
00:19:07,083 --> 00:19:08,583
[MOB gasps]

488
00:19:18,541 --> 00:19:19,791
[RITSU]
What's wrong?

489
00:19:19,875 --> 00:19:21,666
You seem kinda out of it.
Somethin' bothering you?

490
00:19:21,750 --> 00:19:23,458
