491
00:19:23,541 --> 00:19:24,916
Thanks, though.

492
00:19:25,000 --> 00:19:26,791
Sure. Okay then.

493
00:19:29,750 --> 00:19:33,291
[INUGAWA]
Ah! Mob! You actually showed up!

494
00:19:33,375 --> 00:19:34,791
