than I expected,

501
00:19:44,458 --> 00:19:45,583
Vice President!

502
00:19:45,666 --> 00:19:48,125
Well, I had to make
a little extra time

503
00:19:48,208 --> 00:19:49,541
to show this room...

504
00:19:49,625 --> 00:19:50,500
...to them.

505
00:19:50,583 --> 00:19:51,666
[TOME gasps]

506
00:19:51,750 --> 00:19:52,875
[TOKUGAWA]
This will become the club room

507
00:19:52,958 --> 00:19:55,125
of the newly formed
Body Improvement Club.

508
00:19:55,208 --> 00:19:57,583
And they'd like to get
set up as soon as possible.

509
00:19:57,666 --> 00:19:59,541
What? Now, just
hold on a minute!

510
00:19:59,625 --> 00:20:01,708
The Telepathy Club
won't be taken away!

511
00:20:01,791 --> 00:20:04,416
Kageyama was about to sign all
the paperwork needed to join!

512
00:20:04,500 --> 00:20:05,791
Seriously?

513
00:20:05,875 --> 00:20:07,416
Are you out of your mind?

514
00:20:07,500 --> 00:20:08,791
Uh...

515
00:20:08,875 --> 00:20:10,291
Tell me, what grade are you in?

516
00:20:10,375 --> 00:20:11,500
I'm a second year.

517
00:20:11,583 --> 00:20:13,666
Have any experience
in other organizations?

518
00:20:13,750 --> 00:20:14,875
No, I don't.

519
00:20:14,958 --> 00:20:16,333
Do you have a close
friend or love interest

520
00:20:16,416 --> 00:20:17,291
in the Telepathy Club?

521
00:20:17,375 --> 00:20:18,541
I have an acquaintance.

522
00:20:18,625 --> 00:20:19,541
Cram school?

523
00:20:19,625 --> 00:20:20,541
I don't attend.

524
00:20:20,625 --> 00:20:21,291
Do you study?

525
00:20:21,375 --> 00:20:22,416
Not particularly.

526
00:20:22,500 --> 00:20:23,333
[TOKUGAWA]
Any hobbies?

527
00:20:23,416 --> 00:20:24,583
[MOB]
I, uh...

528
00:20:24,666 --> 00:20:26,791
Don't you have anything
at all you want to do?

529
00:20:26,875 --> 00:20:28,041
Huh?

530
00:20:28,125 --> 00:20:29,666
If you let these
students goad you

531
00:20:29,750 --> 00:20:32,041
into joining while having
no interest at all,

532
00:20:32,125 --> 00:20:34,166
what exactly will
you gain from it?

533
00:20:34,250 --> 00:20:35,500
Well, uh...

534
00:20:35,583 --> 00:20:37,750
All I wanna do is live
every day to the fullest.

535
00:20:37,833 --> 00:20:39,833
[TOKUGAWA] Will wasting time
after school with soda,

536
00:20:39,916 --> 00:20:40,916
snacks, and video games

537
00:20:41,000 --> 00:20:43,041
help you "live every day
to the fullest"?

538
00:20:43,125 --> 00:20:46,500
If you want to join this club
of your own free will, go ahead.

539
00:20:46,583 --> 00:20:49,458
However, you should carefully
think this through.

540
00:20:49,541 --> 00:20:52,875
What is it you really
want to do with your life?

541
00:20:52,958 --> 00:20:55,166
[MOB]
What I wanna do...

542
00:20:55,250 --> 00:20:57,791
Do I have anything I wanna do?

543
00:20:57,875 --> 00:21:00,125
Does everyone else
have something?

544
00:21:00,208 --> 00:21:03,625
Something enjoyable?
Something I'm envious of?

545
00:21:03,708 --> 00:21:05,708
What are they enjoying?

546
00:21:05,791 --> 00:21:08,166
Clubs, hobbies, studying?

547
00:21:08,250 --> 00:21:10,791
Now that I think about it,
hanging out with girls

548
00:21:10,875 --> 00:21:12,625
might be fun.

549
00:21:12,708 --> 00:21:13,625
[MOB gasps]

550
00:21:13,708 --> 00:21:15,166
[MOB]
I did have a dream!

551
00:21:15,250 --> 00:21:17,916
I wanted to confess my
feelings to my first love,

552
00:21:18,000 --> 00:21:21,625
Tsubomi, and hold hands
as we walked home.

553
00:21:23,666 --> 00:21:25,291
[MOB]
Take a look, Tsubomi!

554
00:21:25,375 --> 00:21:27,916
When you make frogs float,
they start swimming.

555
00:21:28,000 --> 00:21:30,500
Oh, wow! That's so cute.

556
00:21:30,583 --> 00:21:32,708
[MOB] I can make the bar
all squishy, too.

557
00:21:32,791 --> 00:21:35,250
[TSUBOMI gasps]
You're amazing, Mob!

558
00:21:36,375 --> 00:21:37,500
[MOB]
Look!

559
00:21:37,583 --> 00:21:39,833
I'm only showing you
these things, Tsubomi!

560
00:21:39,916 --> 00:21:41,833
[sighs] I'm getting bored.

561
00:21:41,916 --> 00:21:43,125
[gasps]

562
00:21:44,875 --> 00:21:47,250
[BOY 2B]
The red team can move!

563
00:21:47,333 --> 00:21:49,625
[gunshots]

564
00:21:49,708 --> 00:21:52,666
You're fast, Akira!

565
00:21:52,750 --> 00:21:53,875
[MOB]
That's it...

566
00:21:53,958 --> 00:21:57,125
If I can change anything
by joining a club...

567
00:21:59,291 --> 00:22:01,833
...then I'm gonna join!

568
00:22:01,916 --> 00:22:06,583
Thank you for having me,
Body Improvement Club!

569
00:22:06,666 --> 00:22:08,250
Wait, what'd you say?

570
00:22:09,666 --> 00:22:10,750
Huh?

571
00:22:10,833 --> 00:22:12,750
[MUSASHI]
Welcome aboard! Good to have ya!

572
00:22:12,833 --> 00:22:14,291
[MOB]
Thank you!

573
00:23:49,041 --> 00:23:50,666
[ANCHOR 2A]
Unable to locate the whereabouts

574
00:23:50,750 --> 00:23:52,875
of the suspicious
individual who infiltrated

575
00:23:52,958 --> 00:23:55,083
an all-girls' school
by crossdressing,

576
00:23:55,166 --> 00:23:57,375
the whole area
is on high alert...

577
00:23:59,750 --> 00:24:01,500
[ARATAKA]
Hot!

578
00:24:02,625 --> 00:24:04,333
[ARATAKA] Mob joins the
Body Improvement Club.

579
00:24:04,416 --> 00:24:06,250
On his way home, in an
attempt to be popular,

580
00:24:06,333 --> 00:24:07,333
he goes to the main temple

581
00:24:07,416 --> 00:24:09,000
of an obviously
shady-looking cult.

582
00:24:09,083 --> 00:24:10,125
Are you sure about this, Mob?

583
00:24:10,208 --> 00:24:11,500
Next time, on <i>Mob Psycho 100</i> ,

